Invocation Name: daily intention
des: Daily Intention will help you set a focus for the day. Similar to how yogis set an intention for their practice, Daily Intention will give you something to focus on and guide you through the day. Setting an intention will give you something to work towards and help your day be more fulfilling.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
